NAME
    LWP::Protocol::http::SocketUnixAlt - Speak HTTP through Unix sockets

VERSION
    version 0.0203

SYNOPSIS
      use LWP::Protocol::http::SocketUnixAlt;
      LWP::Protocol::implementor( http => 'LWP::Protocol::http::SocketUnixAlt' );
      ...

DESCRIPTION
    LWP::Protocol::http::UnixSocketAlt is a fork of Florian Ragwitz's
    LWP::Protocol::http::SocketUnix 0.02. It fixes a few issues including:

    *   remedy 'No Host options provided' error

        As suggested in https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=65670

    *   allow specifying URI path

        Currently using "//" as separator, e.g.:
        "http:path/to/unix.socket//uri/path"

SEE ALSO
    LWP, LWP::Protocol

    HTTP::Daemon::UNIX

